{"tid":1930953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［光復連登］連登正式進入內鬥清算手足mode","createTime":"2020-03-18T02:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T21:00:03.000Z","uid":49847,"like":51,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"16b0a57a554b0999d16f412d5653bcc70e33a519","tid":1930953,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:05:01.000Z","msg":"大量黃店俾人話食人血饅頭<br />\n入貨賣消毒用品變晒蟹貨又係人血饅頭<br />\n乜都人血饅頭<br />\n一係就屌邊個邊個係偽黃<br />\n同狗做五缺手勢影相？呃Like 偽黃 起底<br />\n意見不一？屌左你老母先 再話你係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係淺黃港豬？冇問題！踢你出黃 我地好夠人<br />\n再唔係就捉你係五毛公關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇得捉鬼捉第樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心想知入黃色<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經濟</span>圈唔係為左錢係乜 原意本身就係日常消費罷藍捧黃<br />\n<br />\n乜都話人係人血饅頭不如叫黃色善堂圈算啦<br />\n而家做黃絲係政見定係考哈佛？<br />\n門檻去到咩位？做錯少少野就唔認係同路人？<br />\n黃絲夠人喇？咁9月立會贏鳩左啦<br />\n<br />\n先唔理係咪有大量公關入黎帶風向<br />\n最慘係你班友俾人帶到風向先慘<br />\n大把人係真心咁屌自己友<br />\n然後再唔認人地係自己人<br />\n<br />\n槍口對外對準政權唔得咩<br />\n光復左香港喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇見過Save hk班友嘈交？<br />\n仗都未打就清算手足先<br />\n俾你地贏左仲唔變共產黨2.0？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復連登，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n槍口對外，對準政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停止內鬥</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgPtzsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgPtzsv.jpg&h=1dc5161d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1xbxec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1xbxec.jpg&h=1f8cbd59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iF3NP0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiF3NP0T.jpg&h=cb9de77c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9qkqze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9qkqze.jpg&h=3b2089fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a35ddf62bdc2645a005f55aac30a19f11045652a","tid":1930953,"uid":49847,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"連登小測post<br />\n睇下大家想繼續內鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定對準目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087aa05fa7508c20d4de47e2e5b4a8be32721c74","tid":1930953,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9503879126e11b9d12a4f49c7d73bf5e9c51f589","tid":1930953,"uid":49847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"光復連登，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132d73631fa52a2e6d950477ffeeadbb9097f839","tid":1930953,"uid":173072,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de118a80725b65c28412022504438fb5c027d712","tid":1930953,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"光復連登，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83db067415db2be9877f31272ee180219a1d1ac","tid":1930953,"uid":196536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"有個po話班後生仔乞兒<br />\n有成千個like<br />\n連登已淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dd80ade78bd71a0bd08ae613878729eff325c5","tid":1930953,"uid":49847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"中共最驚就係黃圈最想就係分化你地<br />\n你地做足晒 怪邊個<br />\nSor我講野好負面 <br />\n但係係事實"},{"pid":"f0e98d0419c0fe5a0401c6844a6af26211b3